Who: LEGACY, DEEPSTRYKE, PHOBIA, Rat Trap, Quickstride,
Location: Outside the Black Fortress


> Quickstride knew when to turn tail, and this time, he does just as his gut feelings tell him to do. Turn around and bolt as fast as his hooves could take him.
>
> "On second thought Legacy's right! I'M OUTA HERE!"

Legacy slowed slightly as he Quickstride catch up, and then continued
on his way towards the exit, his cannon blasting open any doors that
stood in their way. It was only a mater of minutes before they got to
the main door, it already being open from when they first entered.

Legacy drove across the fallen door that bridged the lava like a draw
bridge and then finally began to slow.

"Tuscon, Rodimus" Legacy transmitted to the two Primes, "Myself, Rat
Trap and Quickstride have successfully escaped the Black Fortress,
where are you located?"

(TAG)

Preston
